headline.main: France's Macron Wants Bank Capital Rules Set by Ministers
headline.print_headline: France's Macron Wants Bank Capital Rules Set by Ministers

lead_paragraph: French presidential candidate Emmanuel Macron said on Monday that he wanted bank and insurance capital rules set by European Union finance ministers rather than by regulators.
